{"recommendationid": "131993389", "author": {"steamid": "76561198031395468", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 15, "playtime_forever": 170, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 170, "last_played": 1674988740}, "language": "english", "review": "This looked like it was going to be an entirely adequate game for the A$17 I paid.  Reading the other reviews here, it seems people's experiences with this have been pretty polarised.  You might be one of the lucky ones; I was not.

