{"recommendationid": "132064540", "author": {"steamid": "76561198125277102", "num_games_owned": 1160, "num_reviews": 34, "playtime_forever": 2122, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 2122, "last_played": 1675290789}, "language": "english", "review": "The idea behind the story was pretty niche, but after completing the game I can't say it had the same feeling as Watch_Dogs. Yes there was oppression, yes it was an underdog style story, but listening to "Wagwam bruv; Hench bruv" and similar young teenage language and phrasing, I found myself hating nearly all the characters I started with and recruited. The personalities behind each character I recruited (which I did QUITE a few) were miserable and unlikable for me. 


