我可能是傻逼，但我不后悔。", "timestamp_created": 1675436529, "timestamp_updated": 1675436529, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 7, "votes_funny": 11, "weighted_vote_score": "0.567743778228759766", "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}

