{"recommendationid": "132320566", "author": {"steamid": "76561198101362986", "num_games_owned": 1915, "num_reviews": 241, "playtime_forever": 54, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 54, "last_played": 1675692949}, "language": "english", "review": "Upside: The gameplay itself feels like the old school game with a team twist to it. You can build your own team. If you get arrested, injured, killed (depending on your difficulty settings) will make you lose a member of your team. Aside from that, nothing much feels different aside from some of the controls being more fluid than previous titles. 

